Package: statplot
Title: Convenient Tools for Generating Standard Statistical Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jaron Arbet", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jarbet@coh.org"))
Maintainer: Jaron Arbet <jarbet@coh.org>
Description: statplot is an R package designed to simplify the creation of common statistical plots. It provides convenient wrapper functions for generating clean, publication-ready visualizations with minimal code. Whether you’re exploring data, performing model diagnostics, or presenting results, statplot helps you focus on analysis rather than plotting details.
